    Page: 453
    Verse: 11
Tags:
  - Suffering
---
God never punishes. Punishment isi always self-inflicted. We bring suffering
on ourselves by our wrong actions. If we are conscious that God is acting
through us, we never do any wrong. We do wrong only when we forget God.
